  "text": "An additional test was run on an environment containing 20 obstacles. Due to various issues, discussed in other work [CITATION_1] , the test was only run up to the main turn, approximately 300m. The results continue to verify the success of the algorithm on the vehicle. For this course, the obstacles were denser than previously tested. The vehicle maneuvered around these obstacles, even when avoiding one collision would normally have led the vehicle toward another. This test demonstrates the algorithm's ability to wind paths between obstacles. Again the vehicle traverses the course while satisfying the corridor constraint and the avoiding obstacles, demonstrating the success of the path planning and the control.",
